            "title": "盤中速報 - 恆生指數上漲748.54點至25865.07點，漲幅2.98%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間08日03:26，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/HSI\">恆生指數</a>上漲748.54點（或2.98%），暫報25865.07點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+1.32%</li><li>近 1 月：-2.49%</li><li>近 3 月：-5.07%</li><li>近 6 月：-6.83%</li><li>今年以來：-2.01%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>銅概念領漲+19.02%。其中    環球戰略集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:08007:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/08007\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">08007-HK</a>)            上漲        71.7%            ;        中國大冶有色金屬(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00661-HK</a>)            上漲        17.65%            ;        五礦資源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01208:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01208\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01208-HK</a>)            上漲        9.78%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>地產代理概念領漲+8.82%。其中    方圓生活服務(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09978:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09978\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09978-HK</a>)            上漲        20%            ;        美聯集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01200:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Arti